get.description: Gets list of Collections based on query parameters. Empty parameter are treated as * and all values are returned. BBox is mandatory

parameters.name: MaxResultCount
parameters.description: MaxResultCount the count of items returned

parameters.name: LandCoverTypes
parameters.description: The optional LandCoverTypes to be selected

parameters.name: CropTypes
parameters.description: The optional CropTypes to be selected

parameters.name: IrrigationTypes
parameters.description: The optional IrrigationTypes to be selected

parameters.name: Bbox
parameters.description: Only features that have a geometry that intersects the bounding box are selected. The bounding box is provided as four decimals:  * Lower left corner, coordinate axis 1 * Lower left corner, coordinate axis 2 * Upper right corner, coordinate axis 1 * Upper right corner, coordinate axis 2  The coordinate reference system of the values is always WGS 84 longitude/latitude (http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/OGC/1.3/CRS84). The values are sequence of minimum longitude, minimum latitude, maximum longitude and maximum latitude.

200.description: fetch the feature with id `featureId` in the feature collection with id `collectionId`

404.description: The requested URI was not found.
